text: KMNO (91.7 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Wailuku, Hawaii. The station is owned by Maui Media Initiative, Inc. It airs a variety radio format. The station was assigned the KMNO call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on August 1, 2012. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * MNO Category:Radio stations established in 2014 Category:2014 establishments in Hawaii Category:Variety radio stations in the United States Category:Maui County, Hawaii
